-- `BLOBS` - Blob operations ✅
-- `WEB_RTC` - WebRTC APIs
-- `CLIPBOARD` - Clipboard API
-- `IFRAME_SCRIPTING` - iframe scripting
-- `DOM_SCRAPING` - DOM scraping
